            The R16,530 Leaderboard Competition
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mt-2 text-slate-500 px-2">
            Compete over 21 days for cash prizes. Two prize rounds keep the race competitive from start to finish.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 my-10 p-6 md:px-10">
            <ServiceCard label="Competition Dates" image={Service1} text="January 12â€“February 1, 2025. 21 days of competition. Start before January 12 to ensure your app is set up correctly and you're ready to compete from day one."/>
